  [Text] We learned from the republic of Srpska army today 
that it has no information on any NATO aircraft action on 
Serbian positions or any part of the territory of our republic 
yesterday, today, or last night, as asserted by UN spokesman 
Major Rob Annink at a news conference in Sarajevo this morning. 
He said that the members of UNPROFOR [UN Protection Force] 
