missiles at the positions of the Serbian fighters and the 
Serbian territory. 
  At the same time, the Army has denied the statement by Rob 
Annink that Serb forces yesterday attacked a Danish humanitarian 
convoy near Teocak. Despite the fact that the convoy was not 
announced, it arrived on the Muslims territory without problems, 
it unloaded humanitarian aid, and went back, again without 
problems. 

