<H3> <TI>   Walesa Denies Olechowski Dismissal Reports </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Walesa Denies Olechowski Dismissal Reports </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2506145194 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1200 
GMT 25 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2506145194 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>
<F P=105>  Polish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] President Lech Walesa has denied reports of the 
possible dismissal of Foreign Affairs Minister Andrzej 
Olechowski. He said during a meeting with journalists that the 
matter has not been considered at all and that he himself will 
not accept Olechowski's departure. Andrzej Olechowski has also 
said that he does not intend to resign and is not going to. 

</TEXT>

