BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Mirza Sadikovic from Bihac] </F>
  [Text] The defense lines on the Bihac and Bosanska Krupa 
fronts as well as on the Grmusko-Srbljanski Plateau have been 
exposed to incessant Chetnik shelling and sniper fire. 
  As for the members of Abdic's traitor phalange, there has 
been no change from the usual, despite the successive defeats 
suffered by that rebel scum. Last night they launched barbaric 
attacks straight after Fikret Abdic -- in the steps of his hero 
Radovan Karadzic -- announced some sort of a counteroffensive. 
From Liskovac, Rosic, and (Crkva), they have been shelling the 
newly liberated areas in the Cazin and Kladusa municipalities 
and, from the Kladusa area, they have been pounding with mortars 
and cannons (Golubovici), [words indistinct]. An entire 
sabotage group was captured during these attacks. 
  Abdic's warmongering headquarters has continued to arrest 
citizens in Velika Kladusa, and to terrorize them. Another 
request has been sent to international organizations for help in 
their protection, since these are people who do not want war and 
who reject the insane ideas of the self-proclaimed Kladusa 
leader. 

</TEXT>

