<H3> <TI>   Six Killed in Muslim Attacks on Serb Areas </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Six Killed in Muslim Attacks on Serb Areas </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806212694 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 2018 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2806212694 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Banja Luka, 28 Jun (TANJUG) -- On several occasions 
today, Muslim forces opened heavy artillery fire from 122-mm 
howitzers on Serb settlements on Mount Vlasic, killing six 
persons, the Information Service of the First Krajina Corps of 
the army of the Serb Republic reported in Banja Luka tonight. 
  In addition to these casualties another 20 people were 
wounded and a great deal of material damage was also inflicted. 
According to military sources, about 30 shells were fired. 
Units of the Serb Republic army were forced to return heavy 
fire in reply to these activities. 
  There has also been sporadic fire in the Srbobran [Gornji 
Vakuf] battlefield from the direction of Prusac. There were no 
casualties in these operations. There was no return of fire to 
these activities. 

</TEXT>

