<H3> <TI>   `Heated Debate' in Parliament Detailed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Heated Debate' in Parliament Detailed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2806201694 Prague CTK in English 1841 GMT 28 Jun 94 -- FOR 
