<H3> <TI>   Italy's Martino Continues `Peace Mission' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy's Martino Continues `Peace Mission' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2806102994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 0948 GMT 28 
Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2806102994 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


