<F P=101> Bulgaria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Airspace `Violation' on 23 Jun Clarified </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Airspace `Violation' on 23 Jun Clarified </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2406181294 Sofia BTA in English 1754 GMT 24 Jun 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU2406181294 </F>
