  [Excerpts] Sofia, June 24 (BTA) -- The units on duty of 
Bulgaria's air force registered a violation of Bulgarian air 
space by 21 light transport aircraft at 10.40 a.m. local time 
[0740 GMT] on June 23, the Defence Ministry's Press Office 
