planes landed at Sofia Airport yesterday [23 June] noon on their 
way back from an exposition in Turkey, it said. The traffic 
controller on duty would not be videotaped. The TV reporter 
learnt from another controller the planes had asked permission 
but the request had arrived late for technical reasons. An 
investigation is underway; this is the reason behind traffic 
controllers' unwillingness to be shown on TV. 

